flowchart TD
    A[User enters Instrument / Capital / Start / End] --> B[Click Run Backtest]
    B --> C[Frontend POST /api/backtest/run]
    C --> D{Request valid?}

    D -->|No| Z[Return 400 error to UI]
    D -->|Yes| E[Build weekday trading-day list]

    E --> F{For each trading day}
    F --> G[Generate deterministic 1-min candles]
    G --> H[Compute EMA5, EMA20, RSI14, IV Rank]
    H --> I[Read values at 09:30]
    I --> J[Select regime + strategy]

    J -->|NO_TRADE| K[Create no-trade result]
    J -->|Trade| L[Build option legs]
    L --> M[Size position]
    M --> N[Minute-by-minute PnL loop]

    N --> O{Exit condition hit?}
    O -->|Profit target| P[Exit]
    O -->|Hard stop| P
    O -->|15:15 EOD| P
    O -->|No| N

    P --> Q[Reprice legs at exit]
    Q --> R[Compute total PnL and result]

    K --> S[Save session to PostgreSQL]
    R --> S

    S --> T{More trading days left?}
    T -->|Yes| F
    T -->|No| U[Commit and return sessions]

    U --> V[Frontend redirects to Dashboard]
    V --> W[Dashboard loads results, summary, trade book]
